中國政府拘捕當知項欠與久美嘉措被許多人權團體譴責。國際特赦組織抗議中國政府拘捕二人，指出久美嘉措可能會再度被折磨<ref name="AI">{{cite web |url=http://www.amnesty.org/en/library/asset/ASA17/011/2009/en/a750242a-f2e7-4fc1-89aa-aaf91ed849f8/asa170112009en.pdf |title=People's Republic of China -Tibet Autonomous Region: A year of escalating human rights violations |format=PDF |date=2009-03-06 |publisher=Amnesty International |accessdate=2013-02-07 |archivedate=2012-12-09 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6ClowSPYH?url=http://www.amnesty.org/en/library/asset/ASA17/011/2009/en/a750242a-f2e7-4fc1-89aa-aaf91ed849f8/asa170112009en.pdf |deadurl=no }}</ref>，並將當知項欠稱為一個[[良心犯|良心犯]]<ref name=AI3 />。[[人权观察|人权观察]]<ref name="HRW">{{cite web |url=http://www.hrw.org/en/news/2009/08/03/china-ensure-fair-trial-tibetan-filmmaker |title=China: Ensure Fair Trial for Tibetan Filmmaker |date=2009-08-03 |archivedate=2012-10-19 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6BX0ErP1j?url=http://www.hrw.org/en/news/2009/08/03/china-ensure-fair-trial-tibetan-filmmaker |publisher=Human Rights Watch |accessdate=2013-02-07 |deadurl=no }}</ref>、[[前線捍衛者|前線捍衛者]]<ref name="AI"/>、[[保護記者委員會|保護記者委員會]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ifex.org/china/tibet/2009/03/19/security_officials_re_arrest_tibetan/ |title=Security officials re-arrest Tibetan filmmaker Jigme Gyatso |date=2009-03-18 |publisher=Committee to Protect Journalists via International Freedom of Expression Exchange |archivedate=2012-10-19 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6BX0KdPTy?url=http://www.ifex.org/china/tibet/2009/03/19/security_officials_re_arrest_tibetan/ |accessdate=2013-02-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>、[[无国界记者|无国界记者]]<ref name="RWB">{{cite web |url=http://en.rsf.org/china-free-dhondup-wangchen-17-06-2009,33443 |title=Free Dhondup Wangchen! |date=2009-06-17 |publisher=Reporters Without Borders |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6BWzLdHBa?url=http://en.rsf.org/china-free-dhondup-wangchen-17-06-2009,33443 |archivedate=2012-10-19 |accessdate=2013-02-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>、以及[[西藏人權與民主中心|西藏人權與民主中心]]<ref name=AI3>{{cite web |url=http://www.amnesty.org/en/library/info/ASA17/033/2009/en |title=China: Tibetan film-maker may face unfair trial, Dhondup Wangchen |date=2009-07-17 |publisher=Amnesty International |deadurl=no |archivedate=2012-10-19 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6BWzPXA3h?url=http://www.amnesty.org/en/library/asset/ASA17/033/2009/en/f56b380f-fd79-4c0b-9b48-927f8e07cc12/asa170332009eng.html |accessdate=2013-02-07 }}</ref>均對中國政府對當知項欠的判決抗議。

於2011年3月10日，前[[美國眾議院議長|美國眾議院議長]][[南希·佩洛西|南希·佩洛西]]呼籲中國政府釋放當知項欠<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P3-2294565831.html |title=Democratic Leader |date=2011-03-10 |publisher=US Federal News Service |accessdate=2013-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160409235927/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P3-2294565831.html |archive-date=2016-04-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。而一個人權和西藏活動人士團體的聯盟亦呼籲釋放當知項欠，並於2012年3月9日在[[紐約市|紐約市]][[時報廣場|時代廣場]]中舉行集會。講者包括當知項欠的妻子拉姆措，以及詩人活動家[[丹增尊珠|丹增尊珠]]。部份《不再恐懼》片段亦於一個12英尺長的視頻屏幕上顯示出來。<ref name=HP>{{cite web |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/natalie-avital/tibet-protests_b_1347560.html |title=State of Control |author=Natalie Avital |date=2012-03-15 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6BX0QywXn?url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/natalie-avital/tibet-protests_b_1347560.html |archivedate=2012-10-19 |work=Huffington Post |accessdate=2013-02-07 |deadurl=no }}</ref>

於2012年，當知項欠獲頒[[國際新聞自由獎|國際新聞自由獎]]<ref name="2012 awards">{{cite web |url=http://cpj.org/awards/2012/ |title=CPJ International Press Freedom Awards 2011 |publisher=Committee to Protect Journalists |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6As7WSZve?url=http://cpj.org/awards/2012/ |archivedate=2012-09-22 |accessdate=2013-02-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。但是，因為當知項欠仍然在囚，所以他無法參與2012年11月的頒獎典禮。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cpj.org/awards/2012/ |title=CPJ International Press Freedom Awards 2012 |date=2012-11-20 |publisher=Committee to Protect Journalists |accessdate=2013-02-07 |archivedate=2012-12-09 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6ClthkRrh?url=http://www.cpj.org/awards/2012/ |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

